Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:03.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是灵树森林的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:04.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还有小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.11,0:00:05.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个大个男人是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.84,0:00:08.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们好像变成观赏物了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:10.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因为前排的人醒目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 是妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.32,0:00:15.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然带着妖精这样奇怪的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:17.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是真正的魔女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.27,0:00:21.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 我可不想和你一起相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:23.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的两位哪个是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:27.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 大家 魔女大人在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:29.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛 鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:30.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:31.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:32.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的小屁孩是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:35.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩根 这到底在开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:37.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:40.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 也难怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:42.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,来一发魔法让他们开开眼如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:44.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙就不会不服气了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:46.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:49.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为了引人注目而使用魔法是不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:52.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我早说了 村长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:53.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,祭司大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.96,0:00:54.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是僧侣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:57.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,事情复杂了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:01:00.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即使依靠魔女这种不可靠的迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:03.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也无法解决目前的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:08.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而且摩根 你让那样的小丫头扮成魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:13.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是打算消除自己一人苟活回来的自责感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:14.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样太肤浅了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:15.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:19.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这副打扮 你们是旅行艺人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:22.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,旅途中被摩根哀求了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:25.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你们是来巡演的还是干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:28.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些魔兽可不是你们能对付的来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:30.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,最好马上离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:32.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可是祭司大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.81,0:01:36.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人仔细看看不是很强壮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:37.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用赶走也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:38.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不可
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:41.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是神明大人给予这个村庄的试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.86,0:01:43.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们唯有祈祷和忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:46.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧 别管他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:49.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们好不容易来了 没进门就被赶走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.66,0:01:50.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好像傻瓜一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:55.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘即使是演戏或假扮也不要如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.77,0:01:58.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这里是圣都 你会被处以火刑的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:02.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女只是堕落和邪恶的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:05.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们带着病人和小孩长途跋涉已经很疲惫了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:08.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话希望借宿一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:10.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 现在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:12.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个姑娘在做祈求恢复的巡礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.26,0:02:16.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,向巡礼者施舍是寺院的规矩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:19.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是死是活我也不会再管了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙你的大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:23.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 那把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:24.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是真家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:25.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个左臂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:28.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,村长 请给他们准备房间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:30.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你想了妙招呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:35.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用眼睛好好感受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:38.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这次邂逅对你到底意何在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家请把这个绑到手指上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,头发吗 是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么把 头发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:19.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能使用念话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:20.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是心灵感应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,念话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:24.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,低能猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:26.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是猴子 你这个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:33.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这里使用的是施术时持有施术对象一部分的被称为感染魔术的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:36.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使用指甲头屋之类的对人下诅咒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:40.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人只要到某种程度 都可能进行直接的思想交互
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:45.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这就需要有很高的气 灵气的磁力的连接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能相连的只有你吗 其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:52.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就和没有修行的人联系是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:59.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因此这次和兽鬼的作战中 希望大家都听我的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:00.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:02.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么 别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:05.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要被你这种小丫头使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是最合适的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:12.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能把握整个战况并传达给大家的只有我这个魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:18.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,确实如此 在兽鬼上魔女才是专家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:22.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样吧 本来她就是对付鬼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:25.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 三等兵向指挥敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:28.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在遇敌前逃跑会被枪毙的 猴子三等兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:30.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想单独待一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:40.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:43.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你在练剑吗 小兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:45.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一个人可不安全啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:48.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老大爷你又在干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:51.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,本想给你们的晚餐准备些鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:52.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 还有番薯汤再忍耐会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:59.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来这里真是个小村庄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:03.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种山谷里 能见阳光的时间不到半天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:11.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我爷爷那辈这个村庄是连着街道的 据说很热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就像你看见的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:18.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这么说 也不想默默等死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你们很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:25.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小兄弟你为何要和他们一起旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.35,0:06:27.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是那位黑色剑士的侍从吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:31.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 我在做武者的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:35.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,格斯大哥和我有约定要教我剑术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那位剑士很强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:41.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,竟能挥舞那样巨大的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:45.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 他强得就和怪物一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:47.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你很崇拜他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,崇拜 别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:51.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是利用他而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:56.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,作为我目前的目标而努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你家里人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个旁人不会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:08.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你又是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:11.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这把年纪还不顾家人去找魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:15.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那些村人是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:20.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对拼命去找魔女的你竟然那么排斥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是群薄情的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:25.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不如也离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:28.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,留在这种小地方也没什么好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.06,0:07:33.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这里长眠着我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:35.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被兽鬼杀害的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:38.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是更久前死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:46.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我感谢把村子命运寄托给我的村民 因此我没有怨言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:53.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我反而更感谢他们 让我在死前能再见到那位魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:56.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,男人都是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:08:00.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我小时候也幻想过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:03.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说着要去找魔女要去抓妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:08.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然后抛下家里的工作去深山里森林里闲逛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:13.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你说的 我也曾要离开这个小村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:17.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自己坐着船从布利达尼斯向海洋出发
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:20.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一直梦想着这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,直到母亲病倒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:28.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的事已经记不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:32.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只知道等察觉到时已经在森林深处迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:37.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为救母亲而去找魔女的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:42.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛在梦中一样 我到了那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:48.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我用带回家的药救回了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:51.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但她已经很衰老了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:57.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,从那以后我就在家做事再也没去过森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:09:00.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,回过神时已经这把年纪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:05.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然后时光流逝 记忆也模糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真的曾见过她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:17.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但魔女却在森林深处等着我 和那时一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:20.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这些对就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:22.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:26.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对我这样的年轻人不要说那种陈年旧事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:28.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,最近的年轻人真是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:32.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把那么普通的一个梦当成年轻时的大事的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:35.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和正在实现野心的我不要相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:37.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的野心会长毛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:39.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:47.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小鬼对你很依赖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:54.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,兽鬼来袭时 村民们能躲藏的就是这个寺院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:57.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然只能在这布阵了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:00.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 我必须要振作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:04.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 寺院坐落的这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:08.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,滚出去 魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:14.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,祭司大人说了 魔女和兽鬼是一个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,让人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在勘察阵地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:24.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:29.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你那时是不是对那个僧侣有话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:31.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对那个臭僧侣才不想说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:34.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是那个僧侣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:38.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为现在世上的人都错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:40.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,坐落着寺院的这个山丘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:44.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,过去曾是祭祀这片土地的精灵的神殿遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法王厅的寺院大都如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:52.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,践踏精灵信仰的圣地然后建立起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:57.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,现在法王厅的教只是用来夸耀自己权力的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:01.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人们礼读着神的名字互相争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:03.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,礼读着神的名字寻求救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:11.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自己想要忘却的东西说不定反而是救赎自己的关键所在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:16.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这里面也有你们魔女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.19,0:11:21.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的师傅过去曾在这附近的村落生活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:24.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,奔走于贫困的村庄之间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,向人们传达精灵的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:31.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一边向他们传教季节的事一边治病救人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:35.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅的魔法救治了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:40.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是随着法王厅的教团扩展到这一带
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:42.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,每个村庄开始建起了寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:45.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,简直如同翻脸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:49.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,人们驱赶师傅 把她赶到了森林里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:56.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,从那之后师傅就在森林中躲避世人并隐居起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:12:01.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在竟然好像没发生过那种事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能原谅这些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:07.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是师傅吩咐谁要救这个村子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:08.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那么不做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:09.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:12.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是没有那个意向的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有必要为了那些讨厌的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:17.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以身犯险了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:19.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个婆婆就要死了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:21.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就更要这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被人说了就算不喜欢也照做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:25.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是小孩的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:30.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个没礼貌还吊儿郎当的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:33.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是不情不愿的来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:37.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个男人不可能是我的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:38.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 不要乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:42.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:46.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,给听不懂话的法尔纳塞小姐绑头发是不是没有意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:49.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是史尔基小姐说要绑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:53.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说念话是靠印象传导的 我也不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:55.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:58.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话这次的兽鬼退治
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:01.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不说起来这次旅行本身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:04.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我都认为应该停止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:08.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:12.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.66,0:13:16.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是变样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:19.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我办不到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:22.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能看见这个笑容的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,应该算是值得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:28.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,风的精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:30.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不被任何东西束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:32.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,能吹到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讽刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:38.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是和我最无缘的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:46.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:47.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:52.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,兽鬼来了 都来寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:53.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:54.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:55.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是心灵传送
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:56.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞尔彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:13:58.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,兽鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.63,0:14:13.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事那个数量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:15.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要一口气吃光我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:17.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧跑吧这里也不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个吹号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,念话马上就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:29.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西确实方便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:31.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我们赶紧去寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:38.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞尔彼高 想想史尔基小姐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,想明白点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:43.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 想像 想像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:48.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们了 精灵们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:14:58.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:14:59.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:07.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:09.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的 有这个就能放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:12.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法 真正的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:15.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 就你一个人出风头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:17.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要出手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:18.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 火焰哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一匹就够了 一匹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:25.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:27.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑啊 要被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,杯水车薪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:34.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:40.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙把受伤的伙伴吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:42.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不想变那样就跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:44.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:51.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:59.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个法尔纳塞小姐会为了别人挺身而出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:03.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看来银的退魔作用生效了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:07.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我来打开退路 赶紧跑到寺院去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:09.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 赶紧进去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊 有人被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:13.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是那些魔女的同行者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:15.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能让我们逃走用身体挡住兽鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:17.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那样就没救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:19.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:20.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我早说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 那些家伙不是人能对付的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:16:58.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在 跑到寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:01.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吗 祭司大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:04.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有那个那个人的话就能从兽鬼手上保护村子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 那家伙好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:10.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不懂哪边是怪物了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,的确不像一般人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:18.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是那个人在精神能轻易影响物质的狭间彷徨的结果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:20.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:23.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,缠在剑周围的那个影子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.32,0:17:25.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗 依巴蕾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:26.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妥妥的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:29.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在你说的方位上都贴好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:30.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,符咒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我说大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:37.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我要用魔法在这个寺院张开防壁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:40.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,全员赶紧进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:41.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个遭报应的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:44.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,村长 赶紧让那个女孩从房顶下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:46.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔术是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我亲眼看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:51.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女孩的同伴隔空砍死兽鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:54.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个剑士大人的同伴们吗 那么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:59.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对对 脚踏实地脚踏实地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:03.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,尤得·海恩 班·海恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:04.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,使不得 使不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:08.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个神的面前做这种邪恶之事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:10.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧从这里下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史尔基是为了谁在做这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:15.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 我叫你停下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:17.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是要住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子正在保护村子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:22.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算生命能延续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:29.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是靠邪门歪道苟且偷生还有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是天命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:34.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个男人 和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:36.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和过去的我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:40.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,仗着神的名义 把人逼上死路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:44.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有反驳的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,光说你也不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:55.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:58.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,诵读咒文的史尔基正在神游天外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:00.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,请把手放开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:01.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要打扰我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:15.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:17.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被包围了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:20.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:21.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:24.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们赶紧去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:26.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这里我一个就够
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,里面的人和女人们拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:30.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:32.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的份也一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:40.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋躲开 过不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:56.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:19:58.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,跳过我们 不对 飞过去的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:20:00.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我们风之军团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:02.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也秀下身手呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:05.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯多洛 这里暂时交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要坦然接受 不能恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:21.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:23.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史尔基
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:25.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 神明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,请引导我到您的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:35.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才就是最后的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:38.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真实的 一群一群的没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,史尔基那小鬼在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:42.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这下不上不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你的本事说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:46.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 这才是关键时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:52.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 身体被剑带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:54.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:55.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:01.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.52,0:21:02.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩根
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:08.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 说你们啊 不能只靠小孩子和老头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:10.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:14.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷子  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:15.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,由虚空中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.74,0:21:20.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把陆 海 空 火的透明的四人之王召唤至此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:22.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以此阵保吾身周全
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:26.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,当温暖的守护的防御之火点亮之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:35.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,令所有灾祸 不会加之吾身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:38.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,本·盖普勒 马鲁可图
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:41.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,马忒·本 盖土鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:47.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,本·欧兰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.15,0:21:49.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法尔纳塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:08.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,兽鬼们 都碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:11.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个光辉是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:15.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口在愈合
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:18.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就有救了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:22.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是 那家伙的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:18.27,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.44,0:00:24.27,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.76,0:01:22.26,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:26.75,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:29.42,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谁猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.47,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:05.52,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:07.80,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,正忙的呢 不能打扰她
Comment: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:31.46,EDChs,,0,0,0,,/--------ED---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:49.15,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}绯红序幕  缓缓拉开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:53.10,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}笑谈之间  揭开舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:57.03,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}台上一切  皆为戏剧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.03,0:23:00.45,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}循序渐进  如诗如画
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.45,0:23:10.04,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}一字之差  终局俱变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:18.52,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}索然无味  其为传说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.10,0:23:23.84,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}利欲之心  隐于夜中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:27.91,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}日升之前  一触即发
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:32.58,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}纯真羽翼  散落人间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:37.28,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}应着之色  是黑是白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.28,0:23:39.36,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}不得而知  好奇尚异
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:43.24,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}余音袅袅  不绝于耳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.24,0:23:47.16,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}何人愿闻  何人可应
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.16,0:23:52.31,EDChs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}虚浮年华  何需再度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:49.15,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}鮮明な赤の緞帳を引く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:53.10,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}歓声の中  舞台へ上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:57.03,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}全て予定調和の戯曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.03,0:23:00.45,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}狂いは無い  絵画の様に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.45,0:23:10.04,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}たった一字が欠けた時に結末は変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:18.52,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}呆気無い程に  それが 物語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.10,0:23:23.84,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}夜に隠したambition  greed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:27.91,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}朝が来る前に放て
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:32.58,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}無邪気に散り降る羽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:37.28,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}染まるべき色は白か黒か
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.28,0:23:39.36,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}知らない  知りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:43.24,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}木霊するostinato
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.24,0:23:47.16,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}誰か聴いて  誰か応えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.16,0:23:52.31,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}仮初の日々はもう要らない
Comment: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:55.35,OPChs,,0,0,0,,/--------OP---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:03:03.17,OPChs,,0,0,0,,刻下的烙印如何磨灭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:12.63,OPChs,,0,0,0,,任凭他人道长短  殊死之斗又何曾徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:22.97,OPChs,,0,0,0,,暗哑了的嘶吼  依旧在耳畔激荡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:29.22,OPChs,,0,0,0,,笑至尽头之人不是我  亦无怨无悔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:33.13,OPChs,,0,0,0,,唯愿能够守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:38.77,OPChs,,0,0,0,,诛尽来敌战至终
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:41.46,OPChs,,0,0,0,,逆天而行破宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:46.40,OPChs,,0,0,0,,思思缠绕神之手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:50.92,OPChs,,0,0,0,,欲断枷锁魂难断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:56.70,OPChs,,0,0,0,,若能终结一切以战止戈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:04:00.21,OPChs,,0,0,0,,焚尽我身又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:08.58,OPChs,,0,0,0,,困兽犹斗  逆境之中寻生存
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:03:03.17,OPJap,,0,0,0,,\h\h\h\h\h\h\h刻まれた烙印は  最早消せはしないと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:12.63,OPJap,,0,0,0,,足掻くだけ時間の無駄だと  誰が言おうと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:22.97,OPJap,,0,0,0,,また聞こえてくる叫び  声にもならない声で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:29.22,OPJap,,0,0,0,,最後に笑うのはおれじゃなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:33.13,OPJap,,0,0,0,,そこにおまえがいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:38.77,OPJap,,0,0,0,,戦いの果てまで辿り着くため
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:41.46,OPJap,,0,0,0,,運命(さだめ)を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:46.40,OPJap,,0,0,0,,断ち切れない  神の手でも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:50.92,OPJap,,0,0,0,,結んだ絆と魂を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:56.70,OPJap,,0,0,0,,戦いの果てまで辿り着くため
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:04:00.21,OPJap,,0,0,0,,すべてを懸けて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:08.58,OPJap,,0,0,0,,足掻き続けて　生き抜いてみせるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.67,0:24:06.50,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an7}这也是报应吗 还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.76,0:24:11.84,Preview,,0,0,0,,我是为了保护他人才挺剑奋起的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:15.43,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}正合我意! 你们这些大猴子们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:19.89,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}比起百人斩来说不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.64,0:24:23.60,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}好想再见你一面啊 好久不见
